title: Oasis - The Plasterman (B-Sides 1994-1998)
description:
Oasis released their b-sides compilation "The Masterplan" 1998.

Plenty of b-sides from the Definitely Maybe/Morning Glory/Be Here Now era were left off however, so I compiled the leftovers into an unofficial follow-up and titled it "The Plasterman" because I'm THAT clever.

320 kbps
